"MLX uses language hints only. Prompt editing is not applied for on-device MLX ASR." = "MLX 仅使用语言提示，不支持在本地 MLX ASR 中应用自由 prompt 编辑。";
"OpenAI ASR uses the resolved main language and a short prompt bias. Keep the prompt concise and focused on recognition." = "OpenAI ASR 会使用解析后的主语言和简短 prompt 偏置。请保持 prompt 简洁，只聚焦识别辅助。";
"GLM ASR uses a short prompt bias. It does not use hotwords in Voxt." = "GLM ASR 使用简短的 prompt 偏置，Voxt 中不使用 hotwords。";
"Doubao ASR uses language hints. Chinese output follows your selected simplified or traditional main language automatically." = "Doubao ASR 使用语言提示。中文输出会自动跟随你选择的简体或繁体主语言。";
"Aliyun ASR uses language hints derived from your selected user languages." = "Aliyun ASR 使用根据你选择的用户语言生成的语言提示。";
"Current model" = "当前模型";
"Simplified Chinese" = "简体中文";
"Traditional Chinese" = "繁体中文";
"Doubao uses App ID + Access Token for streaming API." = "Doubao 流式 API 使用 App ID 和 Access Token。";
"Aliyun ASR in Voxt uses realtime WebSocket only: Qwen models use /api-ws/v1/realtime, Fun/Paraformer models use /api-ws/v1/inference." = "Voxt 中的阿里云 ASR 仅支持 realtime WebSocket：Qwen 模型使用 /api-ws/v1/realtime，Fun/Paraformer 模型使用 /api-ws/v1/inference。";
"Mute other media audio while recording" = "录制时静音其他媒体音频";
"When enabled, Voxt requests system audio recording permission so it can mute other apps' media audio during recording and restore it after transcription completes." = "开启后，Voxt 会请求系统音频录制权限，以便在录制期间静音其他应用的媒体音频，并在转录完成后恢复。";
"System audio recording permission granted." = "系统音频录制权限已授予。";
"System audio recording permission is required for this feature. You can grant it in Settings > Permissions." = "此功能需要系统音频录制权限。你可以在 设置 > 权限 中授予。";
"System Audio Recording Permission" = "系统音频录制权限";
"Required only when muting other apps' media audio during recording is enabled." = "仅当开启“录制时静音其他应用媒体音频”时才需要。";
"Always show rewrite answer card" = "始终显示转写答案卡片";
"Applies only to rewrite. When disabled, the answer card appears only if no writable input is focused. When enabled, rewrite always shows the answer card." = "仅适用于转写。关闭时，只有在未聚焦可写输入框时才显示答案卡片；开启后，转写无论是否聚焦输入框都会显示答案卡片。";
"Whisper" = "Whisper";
"Realtime" = "实时";
"Realtime On" = "实时模式";
"Quality Mode" = "质量模式";
"Whisper translation works only when the ASR engine is Whisper. Voxt will fall back to your saved LLM provider." = "Whisper 翻译仅在 ASR 引擎为 Whisper 时可用。否则 Voxt 会回退到你保存的 LLM 提供者。";
"Whisper translation only supports English output. Voxt will fall back to your saved LLM provider." = "Whisper 翻译仅支持输出英文。否则 Voxt 会回退到你保存的 LLM 提供者。";
"Whisper translation needs a ready Whisper model. Voxt will fall back to your saved LLM provider until the model is ready." = "Whisper 翻译需要可用的 Whisper 模型。在模型准备好之前，Voxt 会回退到你保存的 LLM 提供者。";
"Whisper translation reuses the current Whisper ASR model. It translates speech directly to English and falls back to %@ when Whisper direct translation is unavailable." = "Whisper 翻译会复用当前 Whisper ASR 模型，直接将语音翻译成英文；当 Whisper 直翻不可用时，会回退到 %@。";
"These settings apply to Whisper transcription sessions. Realtime uses WhisperKit's streaming path; turning it off switches to quality-first partial updates." = "这些设置适用于 Whisper 转录会话。开启实时模式时使用 WhisperKit 的流式路径；关闭后会切换为质量优先的 partial 更新策略。";
"The first local Whisper load can take a few seconds. Voxt will show an initializing state in the overlay until the model is ready." = "Whisper 首次在本地加载时可能需要几秒钟。在模型准备好之前，Voxt 会在浮层中显示初始化状态。";
"Keep Resident" = "常驻加载";
"Resident On" = "常驻开启";
"Resident Off" = "常驻关闭";
"When enabled and Whisper is the selected engine, Voxt preloads Whisper after app launch and keeps it resident in memory for faster first use." = "开启后，如果当前选择的是 Whisper 引擎，Voxt 会在启动后预加载 Whisper，并将其常驻在内存中，以加快首次使用速度。";
